SELECT predicted_for AS "time", yhat AS "nn"
FROM (
  SELECT predicted_for, yhat,
         row_number() OVER (
           PARTITION BY predicted_for, model_name, target, horizon_step
           ORDER BY generated_at DESC
         ) AS rn
  FROM predictions
  WHERE model_name = 'aqpy_nn_temperature' AND target = 'temperature' AND horizon_step = 1
) latest
WHERE rn = 1
ORDER BY predicted_for;
